18
00:01:35.890 --> 00:01:41.120
Well, I figured that since I actually have
a degree in film and another degree in business,

19
00:01:41.120 --> 00:01:45.180
maybe I could actually explain this whole
situation in a bit more detail than you’d

20
00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:47.920
usually get in a YouTube comment.

21
00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:53.409
Because it is true that the Chinese government
has very anti-LGBT policies across the nation,

22
00:01:53.409 --> 00:01:58.340
and they’re VERY not fond of any LGBT representation
