Network.

159
00:10:35.910 --> 00:10:37.910
Basically their English Language propaganda
channel.

160
00:10:37.910 --> 00:10:42.860
The news wasn’t even announced on local
Chinese news, only the English Language variant.

161
00:10:42.860 --> 00:10:46.839
