flex how well they were doing economically,

163
00:10:50.800 --> 00:10:56.260
while most of the rest of the world’s cinemas
still stood empty because of COVID 19.

164
00:10:56.260 --> 00:11:00.530
And since there’s no way for Hollywood studios
to confirm these numbers, they’re just forced

165
00:11:00.530 --> 00:11:02.910
to take the Chinese government at its word.

166
00:11:02.910 --> 00:11:06.670
So not only is Hollywood getting a fraction
of the money from China that they do from

167
00:11:06.670 --> 00:11:11.050
the rest of the world, now China is basically
making the argument that while Hollywood apparently

168
00:11:11.050 --> 00:11:15.630
