190
00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:40.949
But even when studios try to work with Chinese
producers, that doesn’t guarantee success.

191
00:12:40.949 --> 00:12:45.930
It just leads to movies doing well in China,
with possibly inflated returns thanks to those

192
00:12:45.930 --> 00:12:48.360
