200
00:13:20.540 --> 00:13:22.990
This is becoming more and more common.

201
00:13:22.990 --> 00:13:27.140
Meanwhile Hollywood, especially Disney, who
got spooked at how poorly the new Star Wars

202
00:13:27.140 --> 00:13:32.110
