203
00:13:32.110 --> 00:13:35.880
in the Middle Kingdom), have been trying to
make movies specifically for China.

204
00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:39.350
The live action Mulan and Marvel’s Shang
Chi come to mind.

205
00:13:39.350 --> 00:13:44.310
But Mulan only made 40 million dollars in
China, and Shang Chi, to this day, still hasn’t

206
00:13:44.310 --> 00:13:45.700
