207
00:13:45.700 --> 00:13:49.780
While not officially stated by the Chinese
government, it’s likely because the movie’s

208
00:13:49.780 --> 00:13:54.160
star, Simu Liu, publicly spoke about how his
family fled China for Canada.

209
00:13:54.160 --> 00:13:56.500
And China doesn’t want that kind of back
talk.

210
00:13:56.500 --> 00:14:00.390
That’s also why, assumedly, Marvel hasn’t
balked at the gay relationship in Marvel’s

211
00:14:00.390 --> 00:14:01.390
